{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"DOMRectReadOnly","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly\"><code>DOMRectReadOnly</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly/DOMRectReadOnly\"><code>DOMRectReadOnly()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly/bottom\"><code>bottom</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly/height\"><code>height</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly/left\"><code>left</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly/right\"><code>right</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly/top\"><code>top</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly/width\"><code>width</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly/x\"><code>x</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly/y\"><code>y</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly/fromRect\"><code>fromRect()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Geometry Interfaces</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMMatrix\"><code>DOMMatrix</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMMatrixReadOnly\"><code>DOMMatrixReadOnly</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMRect\"><code>DOMRect</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><strong><code>DOMRectReadOnly</code></strong>&nbsp;接口通过详细列出&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMRect\"><code>DOMRect</code></a>&nbsp;所使用的标准属性来定义一个属性不可变的矩形。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"构造函数","title":"构造函数","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"domrectreadonly_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly/DOMRectReadOnly\"><code>DOMRectReadOnly()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>用来创建新的 <code>DOMRectReadOnly</code> 对象，但请注意，该构造函数不能由第三方 JavaScript 调用：这样做将返回 “Illegal constructor” 类型错误。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n</dl>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"domrectreadonly.x_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly/x\"><code>DOMRectReadOnly.x</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd><code>DOMRect</code>&nbsp;原点的 x 坐标。</dd>\n <dt id=\"domrectreadonly.y_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly/y\"><code>DOMRectReadOnly.y</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd><code>DOMRect</code>&nbsp;原点的 y&nbsp;坐标。</dd>\n <dt id=\"domrectreadonly.width_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly/width\"><code>DOMRectReadOnly.width</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd><code>DOMRect</code>&nbsp;的宽度。</dd>\n <dt id=\"domrectreadonly.height_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly/height\"><code>DOMRectReadOnly.height</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd><code>DOMRect</code>&nbsp;的高度。</dd>\n <dt id=\"domrectreadonly.top_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly/top\"><code>DOMRectReadOnly.top</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>返回&nbsp;<code>DOMRect</code> 的顶部坐标值（通常与&nbsp;<code>y</code>&nbsp;相同）。</dd>\n <dt id=\"domrectreadonly.right_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly/right\"><code>DOMRectReadOnly.right</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>返回 <code>DOMRect</code> 的右坐标值（通常与 <code>x + width</code>&nbsp;相同）。</dd>\n <dt id=\"domrectreadonly.bottom_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly/bottom\"><code>DOMRectReadOnly.bottom</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>返回 <code>DOMRect</code> 的底部坐标值（通常与 <code>y&nbsp;+ height</code>&nbsp;相同）。</dd>\n <dt id=\"domrectreadonly.left_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly/left\"><code>DOMRectReadOnly.left</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>返回 <code>DOMRect</code> 的左坐标值（通常与 <code>x​​​​​​​</code>&nbsp;相同）。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"静态方法","title":"静态方法","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"domrectreadonly.fromrect_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly/fromRect\"><code>DOMRectReadOnly.fromRect()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>使用指定的位置和尺寸创建一个新的 <code>DOMRect</code> 对象。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"specification","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.fxtf.org/geometry/#DOMRect","title":"Geometry Interfaces Module Level 1"}],"query":"api.DOMRectReadOnly"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.DOMRectReadOnly","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect2\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"其他","title":"其他","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMPoint\"><code>DOMPoint</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"构造函数","id":"构造函数"},{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"静态方法","id":"静态方法"},{"text":"规范","id":"specification"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"其他","id":"其他"}],"summary":"DOMRectReadOnly 接口通过详细列出 DOMRect 所使用的标准属性来定义一个属性不可变的矩形。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"DOMRectReadOnly","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"DOMRectReadOnly","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"DOMRectReadOnly","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/domrectreadonly","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/domrectreadonly/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly","title":"DOMRectReadOnly"}],"pageTitle":"DOMRectReadOnly - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}